The '''Figg family''' consisted of [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] explorer [[Ecclessis Figg/Legends|Ecclessis Figg]], his [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanian]] wife [[Yarith Figg|Yarith]], and their descendants.

The family founded the [[Figg conglomerate]] prior to the exploration of the [[Greater Javin/Legends|Greater Javin]], and maintained control over its holdings through the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

